  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Starship</span>. The Habiki BF3 is a hauler specialised in economic take-off, with <span class=\"name name-technology\">Efficient Thrusters</span> and a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Launch Auto-Charger</span> minimising launch fuel consumption.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一艘专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>。哈比卡BF3是一艘专门的经济用托运船，配备的<span class=\"name name-technology\">高效推进器</span>与<span class=\"name name-technology\">启动自动充能器</span>能够使飞船启动时的燃料消耗降至最低。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收取</span>这艘飞船，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的飞船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上时，使用快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一艘特殊<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>。哈比卡 BF3 拖運船專精於節約起飛成本，並搭載<span class=\"name name-technology\">高效推進器</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">推進系統自動充能器</span>，使燃料消耗最小化。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">領取</span>這艘船加入你的收藏，或是與目前太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，可以利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 召喚太空船。"
  },
